carries this saudade.

1167
01:53:03,543 --> 01:53:04,543
- You know?
- Yeah.

1168
01:53:04,583 --> 01:53:07,583
This kind of... not melancholy,

1169
01:53:07,623 --> 01:53:09,463
but a sadness.

1170
01:53:09,503 --> 01:53:10,863
The longing.

1171
01:53:10,903 --> 01:53:12,943
About longing, you know,

1172
01:53:12,983 --> 01:53:16,703
and nostalgia for things
which cannot and have not been.

1173
01:53:16,743 --> 01:53:18,423
Yeah. Exactly.

1174
01:53:18,463 --> 01:53:22,943
It made it a very unique "African" film,

1175
01:53:22,983 --> 01:53:27,983
